The titles are:

- Hot Tub Time Machine
- Planet of the Apes
- The Time Machine
- Bill and Ted's Excellent Adventure
- Doctor Strange
- Donnie Darko
- Midnight in Paris
- Doctor Who
- Groundhog Day</hint>
			<hint>Shift the first letter by the time zone of the city in that clue. (Use the time zone provided, which should account for summer time where in use.)

EXAMPLE: the first letter is H, and the time zone is UTC+12; shifting H forward in the alphabet by 12 gives the letter T.</hint>
			<hint>The solution is TIME FLIES.</hint>
